{"in": {"title": "Questing Lores", "subtitle": "<span id=\"tr_lore_id\">a blank slate is the best slate</span>", "lines": ["NARRATOR: It was a Thursday. Before then, I knew many people from various backgrounds. Everyone had been able to burn some part of their existence into my very mind and despite how distant these people may be they were able to have their roads meet. It was near the end of my senior year. At this time I made a decision to cut everyone off who had ever managed to intertwine with my highschool life. I figured it was best to move on considering the damage I inadvertently caused, especially during my last two years at the high school.", "ASH: I'm late! Guess I have to skip on the shower.", "NARRATOR: Ash gets dressed and quickly grabs a slice of bread before leaving the front door of his house to go to school. He continues to sprint along the sidewalk until he reaches the school premises.", "ASH: Whew! Just made it in time to pick up my new schedule, it seems most of my classes are scattered across the edges of the campus.&nbsp;", "NARRATOR: Ash continues to attend his classes and during the final hour of the afternoon he heads over to his art class.", "ASH: Alright my last period is art class, I know a couple of my friends are in this class.", "NARRATOR: As he enters the room his eyes are focused on the walls of the room. They were covered with several paintings and drawings of various different styles. The tables were arranged such that 4 people could sit on each of the long sides of each table. The tables were adjacent to each other and stretched horizontally from the point of entry to the end of the room. As he sat down he quickly noticed 2 familiar faces sitting across from him.", "DEREK: Hey! How you been? We haven't seen eachother for a full summer, how was your trip to India?", "ASH: It was great I got to visit many places in Kerala.", "LOGAN: Yo, its been forever dude. This feels just like math class from last year.&nbsp;", "ASH: Yea its good to see you again.", "NARRATOR: The three of them have united after summer break and were catching up with each other describing their hopes for senior year and their future endeavors. To the right of where Ash is sitting is a girl who happened to sneak and take a seat to his right and go unnoticed by the seating arrangement that the art teacher had placed on each table.", "NARRATOR: The teacher had given everyone a task to make a drawing or painting done by the end of class. Ash and the rest of his group all started with their drawings. By the end of the class everyone was instructed to leave their art on their desk area and take a tour around seeing other people's works.", "ASH: Whoa, dang out of everyone in our table I am the most inept. Derek that is one amazing zentangle self portrait you made. The face is whitened and the border is sorrounded by this glistening maple pattern. Yours is so good you're getting an easy A for this.", "DEREK: I honestly had no idea what I was doing I was near a mirror so making a self portrait of my face was the first thing that came to mind.&nbsp; And the zentangles was something I borrowed from one of the arts that are placed on the wall.", "NARRATOR: After everyone in the group admired eachothers works the class soon came to an end. Ash started to walk towards the exit of the blacktop leading to the basketball court after saying bye to his friends at his table."], "speaker_map": {"NARRATOR": "Joanna", "ASH": "Joanna", "DEREK": "Joanna", "LOGAN": "Joanna"}}, "out": {"cache_id": "6ef392b5cf35e5e1b778c6445866252b", "audio_objects": [["3e35fb6eacacdb0838b91510de0d5888-it-was-a-thursday--before---", 0], ["914b4f21059c7daadb7ba600dd580085-i-m-late--guess-i-have-to---", 0], ["3ea9f5c39c4da926e5af1dc19dda9bcd-ash-gets-dressed-and-quic---", 0], ["60b7738f82fb219f6761ff3896c82e22-whew--just-made-it-in-tim---", 0], ["2b8fb7ccf467216e1e77203425b5189e-ash-continues-to-attend-h---", 0], ["8af7d4bec3c4ed08ad0c60655b3f4054-alright-my-last-peri